====== inet-4.x ======

2017-10-09  Zoltan Bojthe

	transportlayer: using insertTransportProtocolHeader(), and fix it

2017-10-04  Zoltan Bojthe

	tcp: more crc fixes

2017-09-14  Levente Mészáros

	All: Removed obsolete TCP socket parameter dataTransferMode from all
	implementations.

	Updated applications and tests.

2017-09-12  Levente Mészáros

	All: Added alias for std::make_shared, std::dynamic_pointer_cast, etc. to
	support replacing the implementation.

	The reason to allow replacing the standard shared pointer is that it uses
	synchronization primitives to achieve thread safety. Thread safety is not
	required for INET simulations.

2017-09-11  Zoltan Bojthe

	~ All: Renamed byte -> B and bit -> b according to IEC & IEEE unit
	conventions.

2017-08-02  Zoltan Bojthe

	ipv4: camelcase: IPv4Header --> Ipv4Header, ICMPHeader --> IcmpHeader

2017-07-05  Levente Mészáros

	All: Followed recent const addition to Ptr<Chunk> in the Packet API.

2017-04-28  Zoltan Bojthe

	tcp: remove kludges

2017-04-06  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Refactored BytesChunk utility functions.

2017-03-29  Levente Mészáros

	Common: Renamed to Packet::getTotalLength and ChunkQueue::getLength.

2017-03-22  Zoltan Bojthe

	~tcp_nsc

